{"tid":1541164,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中英對照解釋點解唔可以接受林鄭嘅解決方法","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:33:09.000Z","uid":28534,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7c92f4d003e02c5a7b6a3f38ecc5940df79872f0","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hARjxDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhARjxDv.jpg&h=e4c568b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【四個解決方法 The four solutions】<br />\n1. 撤回修例 withdrawal of extradition bill <br />\n今日你宣布撤回，為何6月9日100萬人遊行你不撤回，為何6月16日200萬人遊行你不撤回？ <br />\nYou withdraw the bill today. Why didn't you withdraw after the 1 million demonstration on 9th June? Why didn't you withdraw after the 2 millions demonstration on 16th June? <br />\n2. 委任兩名人士進入監警會 Appointing 2 extra members into IPCC <br />\n委任兩名親建制人士進入一個有名無實無權無力的監警會，搵笨呀？<br />\nYou appoint 2 pro-establishment persons into IPCC which has no power to oversee the Police force. Are you joking?<br />\n3. 走入社區聆聽市民心聲 Walking into the society to listen<br />\n你的日常工作就是要聆聽市民的心聲，以及回應訴求。你將你的工作當作解決方法，又搵笨呀？<br />\nYour duty is to listen and respond to people&rsquo;s opinion. You use your duty as a solution, are you joking again?<br />\n4. 邀請各界專業人士就社會深層次問題進行研究及檢討 Inviting professionals from different sectors to investigate the deep-rooted problems of the society<br />\n你的甚麼甚麼委員會不就是研究檢討這些問題嗎？你又想搵香港人笨呀？曬氣啦﹗<br />\nYour different committees are serving the purpose to investigate the problems. Are you still joking us?<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n#曬氣啦"},{"pid":"e94814223675028e2f24f42d3927dad60ffa0165","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n1"},{"pid":"97b86433e699dbfb0a16fbfb9b61fde023813949","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"91a0