s/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地真係就輸啦<br />\n<br />\n1. 同我Like 全部手足post<br />\n手足d post 最多得1000 幾個likes <br />\n成個連登得1000人做Twitter 文宣？<br />\n<br />\n2. 同留言既外國人解釋我地未贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 留言希望國會議員通過人權法<br />\n英文差可以參考其他人既comments再改幾隻字"},{"pid":"0bccdd7957e67d7f903485c576ed407681d6726f","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d0a41f2e314dc3291a2ac21cad2c24871f1b6ebc","tid":1541164,"uid":212182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"你地係咪仲天真以為呢個政府值得我地信任？仲信政府既承諾？點解唔向非法管治香港既中共說不？點解唔可以拎返主動權？點解仲甘願做中共奴隸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOQLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOQLuS</a><br />\n要記住，香港唔係一個地方，係住呢度既人！我地先係香港既核心，香港既主人！無左我地，政府根本唔係一回事！點解要比依個草菅人命既政府拖住鼻子走！<br />\n有人以為宣告一國兩制同中英聯合聲明失效就會無西方國家幫手，其實唔啱<br />\n只要你將呢場運動變成自由民主vs極權主義<br />\n外國係無得唔幫。9月8日，不見不散！"},{"pid":"6bdcd96044727dc6e8d492be7ca614471506a23a","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d6f1ba3d9d70459d04ed0edde1b9133c91697b55","tid":1541164,"uid":261300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"借位推post <br />\n[膊頭有花入]大家應該調轉分析下，林鄭撤回將會係我地connect對家既最好時機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540580</a>"},{"pid":"7aa93953fa428a186444ead279c53d6c2d901354","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a14dbd019e92b2ea650d39b56f37bfc2ec8f923f","tid":1541164,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"04ac0ec8c77386c101417815f0a6225993ae9477","tid":1541164,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:49:12.000Z","m